<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Game Inventory</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="/images/watermelon.png">
        <span>Gamers</span>
    </div>

    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/items">Products</a>
        <a href="/categories">Categories</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="search">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Search products...">
        <button>Search</button>
    </div>
</header>

<main class="container">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>

    <p class="intro">
        Welcome to Gamers! Where all of your inventory needs are met. Here,
        you have full control over your products. You can add any product or
        category for your store, complete with color coding and custom images!
        Give it a try and be sure to leave a review in the app store!
    </p>

    <a href="/items" class="card products">
        view games →
    </a>

    <a href="/categories" class="card categories">
        view categories →
    </a>
</main>

</body>
</html>